name: Pre-Order Finesse Leather Branded Beanie (Red)
description:
The official Finesse Winter Beanie.

This hat features genuine leather branded with our Finesse Clothing logo and hand sewn into a premium cotton beanie. This premium hat will top off any outfit.

name: Finesse at its Finest Crewneck (Women's)
description:
Cut to specifically fit a woman's curves and made from a 50/50 cotton poly blend, this shirt perfectly balances fit, feel and durability. It also includes air jet yarn for softer feel and no pilling. This shirt features our new "Finesse at its Finest" logo in white and hot pink that really pop on the black sweatshirt. Its additional details include our Finesse Clothing tag on the back of the neck and our custom hem tags sewn into the bottom left hem. Like all of our shirts it also utilizes printed neck tags instead of sewn tags for extra comfort.

*Preshrunk fleece to prevent shrinkage.

name: *New Arrival* FTW Fashion Tee (Black, Red, & White)
description:
The staple of our Finesse the World collection, Finesse Clothing presents the FTW fashion tee. 

Made of 100% combed ringspun cotton for a premium feel and fashion cut for a modern stylish fit, this shirt is top of the line. It features our globe logo in white with contrasting red stars over a black shirt. Its additional details include our Finesse Clothing tag on the back of the neck and our custom hem tags sewn into the left sleeves. Like all of our shirts it also utilizes printed neck tags instead of sewn tags for extra comfort. 

*Preshrunk to prevent shrinkage.
